{
  "name": "Powerful Maneuvers (EitR)",
  "type": "feat",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You are skilled at pushing your foes around.</em> <br /><br /></p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong></p>\n<p>Str 13, base attack bonus +1.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p class=\"stat-block-1\">You do not provoke an attack of opportunity when performing a bull&nbsp; rush, hamstring, overrun, or sunder combat maneuver. In addition, you receive a +2 bonus on checks with these combat maneuvers. You also receive a +2 bonus to your Combat Maneuver Defense whenever an opponent tries to bull rush, hamstring, or overrun you or sunder your gear.</p>\n<p class=\"stat-block-1\">Targets of your overrun attempts may not choose to avoid you.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Normal</strong></p>\n<p class=\"stat-block-1\">You provoke an attack of opportunity when performing&nbsp; a&nbsp; bull&nbsp; rush,&nbsp; hamstring,&nbsp; overrun,&nbsp; or&nbsp; sunder&nbsp; combat maneuver.</p>",
